title: Nassau County World AIDS Day Conference 2015
desc: The Nassau County World AIDS Day Conference 2015 will provide all community members with resources, support, and information about the most recent medical advancements in the treatment and prevention of HIV/AIDS. ?The Conference will include Free HIV Screening, Health Insurance Information, as well as mental health resources. Our Keynote address will be given by Dr. Monica Sweeney, MD, MPH, FACP - Vice Dean for Global Engagement, and Clinical Professor and Chair of the Department of Health Policy & Management in the School of Public Health at SUNY Downstate.
